===Noun===
'''octane'''

#{{chemistry}} Any member in a group of [[metametric]] [[hydrocarbon]]s (C<sub>8</sub>H<sub>18</sub>) of the [[methane]] series. The most important is a colourless, volatile, inflammable liquid, found in [[petroleum]].

